            <p><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/games/pokemon-champions">Pokémon Champions</a> will be receiving some substantial bug fixes in upcoming patches, developer The Pokemon Works has announced.</p>
<p>Announced in <a href="https://news.pokemon-home.com/ja/page/758.html">a new blog post</a>, these changes affect certain moves which weren't working correctly, mega evolutions problems, and incorrect genders for certain tutorial Pokémon .</p>

<figure>
<p>
